<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She bared all for a good cause on The All New Monty: Guys &amp; Gals on Sunday night.</p>

<p>And on Monday, radio presenter Ash Pollard took a stroll with her baby daughter, whose name she is yet to reveal, near her home on the NSW Central Coast.</p>

<p>The 34-year-old, who welcomed her firstborn on Friday, shared a sweet photo to Instagram of herself pushing her baby in a stroller.</p>

<p>Baby's first stroll! On Monday, radio presenter Ash Pollard took a walk with her baby daughter, whose name she is yet to reveal, near her home on the NSW Central Coast</p>

<p>She posed in compression tights and a puffer jacket, and also wore a face mask.</p>

<p>'How do the influencers do it?' she wrote in the caption, adding that her daughter's pram was her 'new wheels'.</p>

<p>'You don't see them rocking compression stockings. Need new gear to reach MILF status,' she added.</p>

<p>Adjusting to motherhood: 'How do the influencers do it?' Ash asked her Instagram followers, adding that her daughter's pram was her 'new wheels'</p>

<p>Just hours earlier, viewers had watched her strip off on The All New Monty to raise awareness of early detection and prevention of cancer.</p>

<p>The burlesque show had been filmed at Sydney's Enmore Theatre in March, at about the same time she discovered she was pregnant.</p>

<p>She was joined on stage by the likes of showbiz legend Patti Newton, Home and Away star Sam Frost, singer Danielle Spencer and model Erin Holland.</p>

<p>Baring all: Just hours earlier, viewers had watched Ash (left, with Danielle Spencer) strip off on The All New Monty to raise awareness of early detection and prevention of cancer</p>

<p>Brave: The burlesque show had been filmed in Sydney in March, at about the same time she discovered she was pregnant. Pictured (L-R) Patti Newton, Ash Pollard, and Danielle Spencer</p>

<p>Ash, who is known for her appearances on My Kitchen Rules and I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, shares her daughter with partner Pete Ferne.</p>

<p>The pair have been together for two years, and Ash announced her pregnancy to her boyfriend live on stage while filming The All New Monty.</p>

<p>Monday's post comes after Ash announced the birth of her first child on Friday.</p>

<p>She shared a black-and-white image of herself cradling the newborn, who was seen grabbing Pete's finger while lying on Ash's chest under a blanket.</p>

<p>'She's here! #Obsessed,' the former reality star wrote in the caption. </p>

<p>New parents: Ash, who is known for her appearances on My Kitchen Rules and I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, shares her daughter with partner Pete Ferne (right)</p>

<p>Smitten: Monday's post comes after Ash announced the birth of her first child on Friday. She shared this black-and-white image of herself cradling the newborn, who was seen grabbing Pete's finger while lying on Ash's chest under a blanket</p>
